BitCoin implemented in perl, meant to be portable.

Usage:
    perl bitcoin.pl

Features:
- web interface
- data stored in sql via DBI (sqlite by default)
- blockchain download
- chain branches
- key management with confirmed amount and unconfirmed delta

"Do what you want" license.

Work in progress on multisig
 eb3b82c0884e3efa6d8b0be55b4915eb20be124c9766245bcc7f34fdac32bccb

delete broken block to reload and reapply it again:
 delete from blk where hash=(select hash from blk where nheight=-1 order by ntime asc)

links:
 https://en.bitcoin.it/wiki/Protocol_specification
 https://github.com/bitcoin/bips
 https://bitcoin.org/en/developer-examples#p2sh-multisig

